html\">funerary</term>\n                </keywords>\n            </textClass>\n        </profileDesc>\n        <revisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            <listChange>\n                <change when=\"2016-12-03\" who=\"#JCu\">James Cummings autogenerated EpiDoc output from database</change>\n                <change when=\"2019-07-15\" who=\"#AA\">Alex Antoniou Epidoc editing and English translation</change>\n            \t   <change when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode</change>\n            \t   <change when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages</change>\n            \t<change when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers</change>\n\t\t<change when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography</change>\n\t    <change when=\"2020-12-18\" who=\"#system\">Updated Zenodo DOI</change>\n            \t<change when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references</change>\n                <change when=\"2022-10-31\" who=\"#martaf\">Marta Fogagnolo revised the text encoding, added dimensions, translations and commentary</change>\n\t</listChange>\n        </revisionDesc>\n    </teiHeader>\n    <facsimile>\n        <surface type=\"front\">\n            <graphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001351_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                <desc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana</desc>\n            </graphic>\n            <graphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001351.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                <desc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana</desc>\n            </graphic>\n         </surface>\n    </facsimile>\n    <text>\n        <body>\n            <div type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#martaf\">\n                <ab>\n                    <lb n=\"1\"/><g ref=\"#christogram\">☧</g>\n                    <lb n=\"2\"/><w>Ἐνθάδε</w> <w>κεῖτε</w> <persName type=\"attested\"><name>Δόξα</name></persName>\n                    <lb n=\"3\"/><w>ζήσασα</w> <w>ἔτη</w> <num value=\"28\"><hi rend=\"supraline\">κη</hi></num>\n                    <lb n=\"4\"/><w>τελευτᾷ</w> <w>τῇ</w> <w>πρὸ</w> <gap reason=\"lost\" unit=\"character\" quantity=\"1\"/>\n                    <lb n=\"5\"/><w><expan><abbr>καλ</abbr><ex>ανδῶν</ex></expan></w> <w><expan><abbr>Ὀκτωβ<supplied reason=\"lost\">ρ</supplied></abbr><supplied reason=\"lost\"><ex>ίων</ex></supplied></expan></w>\n                    <lb n=\"6\"/><orig><unclear>ΛΣ</unclear></orig><orig>ΣΑ</orig><gap reason=\"illegible\" unit=\"character\" quantity=\"1\"/><orig>Λ</orig><orig><unclear>ΤΗΗ</unclear></orig><gap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                </ab>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"apparatus\" resp=\"#martaf\">\n                <listApp>\n                    <app><note>Text based on photographs</note></app>\n                    <app loc=\"line 2\"><note>Δόξα lapis, Korhonen; Terramuzza: Δόλα; Ferrara, Wessel: Δόζα; Kirchhoff, Kaibel: Δό<corr>μν</corr>α; Ferrua: Δοία (= Gemina)</note></app> \n                     <app loc=\"line 5\"><note>Wessel: ὀκτω<supplied reason=\"omitted\">β</supplied>[ρίων</note></app>\n                     <app loc=\"line 6\"><note>Torremuzza: ..ΛΤΗΩ; Kirchhoff: ἡμέρᾳ ---; Kaibel: fortasse consules fuerunt; Ferrua: ΖΗΣΑΣΑ ΤΗΝΗ; Korhonen: <unclear>ΛΣΣΣΟ</unclear>Λ<unclear>ΤΗ</unclear>ΙΙ[---] </note></app> \n                </listApp>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#martaf\">\n                <p>((Chi-Rho)) Here lies Doxa, having lived for 28 years. She died [-] before the Kalends of October…</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"#martaf\">\n                <p>((Chi-Rho)) Qui giace Doxa, avendo vissuto per 28 anni. Morì [-] prima delle Calende di ottobre…</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"commentary\" resp=\"#martaf\">\n                <p>This Christian epitaph has the traditional formula <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">ἔνθαδε κεῖται</foreign>, the name of the deceased, the age and the date of death indicated by <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">τελευτάω</foreign> in the present form (see Korhonen 2004: 105-107). The last line is severely damaged and illegible, and Korhonen speculates that it may be a (later) graffito addition. The reading of Korhonen of the name of the deceased, <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">Δόξα</foreign>, is the only plausible reading, since Ferrua’s reading <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">Δοία</foreign> (from the Latin <foreign xml:lang=\"la\">Gemina</foreign>) is not otherwise attested (pace LGPN 3A: 133), nor is Terramuzza’s reading <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">Δόλα</foreign> and Ferrara’s reading <foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">Δόζα</foreign> (<foreign xml:lang=\"grc\">Δόμνα</foreign> is palaeographically improbable).</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"bibliography\">\n                <listBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    <bibl>\n                        <author>Torremuzza</author>\n                        <date>1769</date>\n                        <citedRange>247 no.23</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/SPTB56H3\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl>\n                        <author>Torremuzza</author>\n                        <date>1784</date>\n                        <citedRange>264 no.27</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/7PSFHSUH\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl>\n                        <author>Ferrara</author>\n                        <date>1829</date>\n                        <citedRange>391 no.3</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/82T4IWDN\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IG\">\n                        <citedRange>\n                            <ref target=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\">14.0532</ref>\n                        </citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q2SBPG9F\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IMusCatania\">\n                        <citedRange>182</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EUC82DH\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIG\">\n                        <citedRange>4.9482</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/HTUDQBXS\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001252\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001252</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IGCVO\">\n                        <citedRange>1360</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/9CT5ZWIK\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl>\n                        <author>Ferrua</author>\n                        <date>1989</date>\n                        <citedRange>no.439</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/759ZXHKQ\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995</ref></bibl>\n                </listBibl>\n\t   <listBibl type=\"discussion\">\n\t       <bibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IMusCatania\">\n\t           <citedRange>105-107</citedRange>\n\t           <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EUC82DH\"/>\n\t       <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</ref></bibl>\n\t   </listBibl>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>\n",
